{"type": "article", "id": 25367, "title": "带有大理石圆边桌的皮椅", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-13T07:14:50Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606071048493ewUjqINfsx9yYd2.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这张长椅带有小型的圆边桌，是瑞典设计团队 Afteroom 为丹麦家居品牌 Menu 设计的。椭圆形的座位面采用了皮革，结构是很细的金属管，在中间的位置连接了大理石的圆桌面，两者之间也构成了一种对比和平衡，很典雅。他们曾经发布了一个带有三只腿的椅子与此类似，可以适合家庭或餐厅等多个场合。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104847JOlwrHdI4VfikAB8.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.23931624\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104848BnKkumgVc90zifJZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.80128205\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071048482RcmkfUNiptTBLWq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68269231\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104849yi2ba3DWcE50wUoJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}